Kiersten Warren https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kiersten_Warren 0 Kiersten Nicolla Dale Warren (born 4 November 1965) is an American actress. Her best known roles include Alex Tabor on Saved by the Bell: The College Years and Nora Huntington on Desperate Housewives.
